    <briefdescription>
<para>GUI authentication implementation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Fixed built-in credential for the clinical workstation login screen. The credential is compiled in; no external credential store or network call is made, satisfying the static-memory requirement (SYS-012).</para>
<para>Default login: username = admin password = Monitor@2026</para>
<para>@req SWR-GUI-001 @req SWR-GUI-002 </para>
